Invocation Name: movie quiz
des: It is a movie-quiz that involves individuals of all ages. An individual will be asked five questions and is supposed to make a correct guess of the movie, when Alexa prompts with a famous dialogues of the movie to be guessed. On a correct guess, the individual will be awarded a point by Alexa. The individual with the highest number of correct guesses will be the winner!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
